#. oFoGj
#: chapter_numbering.xhp
msgctxt ""
"chapter_numbering.xhp\n"
"par_id3147782\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the heading level that you want to assign to the custom paragraph style in the <item type=\"menuitem\">Level</item> list."
