msgstr "Arrastre el elemento donde desee insertar el hiperenlace en el documento."

#. VKcyG
#: hyperlinks.xhp
msgctxt ""
"hyperlinks.xhp\n"
"par_id3149635\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The name of the item is inserted in the document as an underlined hyperlink."
